    "main_contenedor_bloque_eventos_columna_w4VTkz": {
      "type": "main-contenedor-bloque-eventos-columna",
      "blocks": {
        "bloque_multicolumna_wGzkc4": {
          "type": "bloque_multicolumna",
          "settings": {
            "top_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Image-event-blog.jpg",
            "block_background_color": "#f5f5f5",
            "transparent_background": true,
            "title_date_event": "October 22-24, 2025 - Ferndale and Crescent City, CA",
            "title_color_date_event": "#002554",
            "title_bloque": "Join us at:",
            "clase_title_bloque": "Titulo-Nickson-four-h3",
            "title_color_bloque": "#9a7a4b",
            "subtitulo_bloque": "North Coast Farm to School Nutrition Director Workshop",
            "clase_subtitulo_bloque": "Titulo-Nickson-four-h3",
            "subtitulo_color_bloque": "#002554",
            "text": "<p>We’ll host a three-day training and workshop in Northern California with tours of our facility and local farms. The days will consist of panel discussions, scratch cooking and stops at local producer owned businesses. Our goal is to connect Nutrition Directors to resources needed to self-certify and navigate procurement for their districts. Our co-host will be Foggy Bottom Boys, one of our 20+ family-owned farm suppliers.<\/p>",
            "text_color": "#002554",
            "mostrar_boton": false,
            "texto_boton": "Text",
            "enlace_boton": "",
            "color_boton": "#002554"
          }
        },
        "bloque_multicolumna_4bKVwQ": {
          "type": "bloque_multicolumna",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "top_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Image-event-blog-2.jpg",
            "block_background_color": "#f5f5f5",
            "transparent_background": true,
            "title_date_event": "Date TBA - Southern California",
            "title_color_date_event": "#002554",
            "title_bloque": "Join us at:",
            "clase_title_bloque": "Titulo-Nickson-four-h3",
            "title_color_bloque": "#9a7a4b",
            "subtitulo_bloque": "K-12 Farm to School Summit",
            "clase_subtitulo_bloque": "Titulo-Nickson-four-h3",
            "subtitulo_color_bloque": "#002554",
            "text": "<p>This is a one-day immersive experience held in Southern California to bring together local Farmers, School Nutrition Directors and Farm to School Community partners. The day will include panels, fireside chats and interactive learning experiences with partners such as the Alice Waters institute, Chef Ann Foundation and the CDFA. Our goal is to model farm to school solutions that scale.<\/p>",
            "text_color": "#002554",
            "mostrar_boton": false,
            "texto_boton": "Text",
            "enlace_boton": "",
            "color_boton": "#002554"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "bloque_multicolumna_wGzkc4",
